WEBVTT

00:00:20.090 --> 00:00:20.890
You're awake?

00:00:22.510 --> 00:00:24.110
I knew it wasn't like this.

00:00:24.850 --> 00:00:26.090
You wouldn't do this.

00:00:31.110 --> 00:00:32.409
My guess was right.

00:00:33.640 --> 00:00:35.970
Shrimpie has two consciousnesses in his mind.

00:00:35.970 --> 00:00:37.760
I don't know why,

00:00:38.210 --> 00:00:39.740
But besides his original self,

00:00:39.740 --> 00:00:41.520
There's another dark presence inside him—

00:00:41.520 --> 00:00:42.280
Like

00:00:43.490 --> 00:00:45.140
Two completely separate personalities.

00:00:45.140 --> 00:00:46.170
They

00:00:46.890 --> 00:00:49.500
Share sight, hearing, and touch,

00:00:50.700 --> 00:00:53.000
But they don't know each other's memories or thoughts.

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:54.130
I call that evil side

00:00:55.250 --> 00:00:56.680
"Dark Shrimp."

00:00:57.600 --> 00:00:58.840
He's been watching

00:00:59.380 --> 00:01:02.040
And controlling Shrimpie's body all this time.

00:01:03.380 --> 00:01:04.310
Most of the time,

00:01:05.349 --> 00:01:07.480
Shrimpie is like a prisoner trapped inside his own mind,

00:01:07.480 --> 00:01:08.680
He can't do anything.

00:01:13.640 --> 00:01:14.640
Did he go crazy

00:01:15.070 --> 00:01:16.280
From snake venom?

00:01:18.430 --> 00:01:20.250
It sounds crazy, right?

00:01:21.570 --> 00:01:22.940
I would go crazy too.

00:01:23.370 --> 00:01:25.200
But he never gave up—

00:01:25.930 --> 00:01:27.480
He's been fighting back this whole time.

00:01:27.480 --> 00:01:30.200
And this Dark Shrimp seems to be plotting something huge.

00:01:30.200 --> 00:01:31.640
Shrimpie wants to stop him

00:01:31.640 --> 00:01:32.590
From killing him.

00:01:32.590 --> 00:01:34.830
But if that other consciousness takes control of his body—

00:01:34.830 --> 00:01:37.430
Then wouldn't he be unable even to kill himself?

00:01:37.430 --> 00:01:40.690
So how is he supposed to destroy that other consciousness?

00:01:40.759 --> 00:01:42.160
You're Mo Yungao, right?

00:01:42.430 --> 00:01:43.680
Your men are all dead.

00:01:44.729 --> 00:01:46.330
The Hidden Thread strategy.

00:01:47.259 --> 00:01:48.750
I set up a clue,

00:01:49.070 --> 00:01:49.729
And

00:01:50.570 --> 00:01:53.370
You'll follow this clue to think and investigate,

00:01:53.450 --> 00:01:54.780
And reach a conclusion.

00:01:55.350 --> 00:01:56.370
But in reality, both the conclusion

00:01:56.370 --> 00:01:58.229
And the entire chain of reasoning

00:01:58.370 --> 00:01:59.340
Were traps

00:02:00.290 --> 00:02:02.090
I laid out for you from the start.

00:02:03.230 --> 00:02:04.890
Shrimpie wants to set up a trap

00:02:05.220 --> 00:02:06.700
Convincing enough that Dark Shrimp will believe it completely

00:02:06.700 --> 00:02:08.229
And end up killing himself.

00:02:09.130 --> 00:02:10.930
And when that happens, Shrimpie

00:02:11.460 --> 00:02:12.870
Will die with him.

00:02:17.900 --> 00:02:19.310
But wouldn't Dark Shrimp know everything

00:02:19.310 --> 00:02:20.600
Zhang Haixia does?

00:02:21.410 --> 00:02:23.270
He can't let him notice anything.

00:02:24.130 --> 00:02:25.400
How is that possible?

00:02:26.520 --> 00:02:27.530
Now two consciousnesses

00:02:27.530 --> 00:02:29.260
Are fighting for the same body.

00:02:29.620 --> 00:02:32.020
Dark Shrimp wants to wipe out Shrimpie's consciousness.

00:02:32.020 --> 00:02:33.530
Shrimpie needs to let Dark Shrimp

00:02:33.530 --> 00:02:35.190
Know where his weakness is,

00:02:35.280 --> 00:02:37.010
Which is the way to wipe him out.

00:02:37.680 --> 00:02:38.360
Step two,

00:02:39.680 --> 00:02:41.340
Shrimpie pretends not to know

00:02:41.690 --> 00:02:42.579
And reacts as usual.

00:02:42.579 --> 00:02:45.110
This way, Dark Shrimp will fall into the trap.

00:02:45.470 --> 00:02:47.600
Shrimpie's weakness is me and Mentor.

00:02:49.530 --> 00:02:51.140
If his closest ones

00:02:52.530 --> 00:02:53.430
Betray him

00:02:54.300 --> 00:02:55.280
And abandon him,

00:02:56.680 --> 00:02:58.270
It's fatal to him.

00:03:06.420 --> 00:03:08.740
So this Dark Shrimp goes around killing people

00:03:08.740 --> 00:03:10.600
And intentionally shows it to me.

00:03:11.620 --> 00:03:13.630
Sometimes it even pretends those killings are for my sake.

00:03:13.630 --> 00:03:14.910
It's trying to provoke me,

00:03:14.910 --> 00:03:16.090
To push me away from him,

00:03:16.090 --> 00:03:17.150
To make me hate him—

00:03:18.370 --> 00:03:19.970
So Shrimpie will break down.

00:03:24.720 --> 00:03:25.720
The cruelest part

00:03:26.579 --> 00:03:28.050
Of this trap is here.

00:03:28.870 --> 00:03:30.740
Obviously it's a trap he set himself,

00:03:30.740 --> 00:03:32.400
But he has to be in it too,

00:03:32.740 --> 00:03:34.710
And helplessly watch himself

00:03:36.470 --> 00:03:37.329
Being tortured

00:03:38.410 --> 00:03:39.210
Until he dies.

00:03:40.750 --> 00:03:41.950
He can't do anything.

00:03:43.390 --> 00:03:44.420
Then doing this

00:03:44.740 --> 00:03:47.090
Can only kill Zhang Haixia's consciousness.

00:03:47.090 --> 00:03:49.250
How do we kill Dark Shrimp's consciousness?

00:03:49.250 --> 00:03:51.470
I guess he needs me to cooperate with him.

00:03:51.470 --> 00:03:52.300
Then how

00:03:53.060 --> 00:03:54.090
Do you cooperate?

00:04:03.920 --> 00:04:06.440
Now I need to know what Dark Shrimp is,

00:04:07.930 --> 00:04:09.220
What his weakness is,

00:04:09.250 --> 00:04:10.650
And more of his memories.

00:04:26.920 --> 00:04:28.220
Was he crazy just now,

00:04:28.620 --> 00:04:30.180
Talking nonsense all the time?

00:04:30.180 --> 00:04:31.750
But if what he said is true,

00:04:33.620 --> 00:04:34.740
Then Zhang Haixia

00:04:37.650 --> 00:04:38.820
Is too pitiful.

00:04:52.730 --> 00:04:53.440
Shrimpie!

00:06:19.010 --> 00:06:25.620
[Archives: The Nanyang Mystery]

00:06:25.890 --> 00:06:28.570
[Episode 33]

00:07:47.950 --> 00:07:49.159
These murals

00:07:50.680 --> 00:07:53.280
Record the history of the ancient Wupi people.

00:07:54.130 --> 00:07:57.060
I should be able to find the origin of the Dark Shrimp.

00:07:58.000 --> 00:07:59.010
These tribes

00:07:59.030 --> 00:08:01.960
Lived in the southwestern rainforests year-round,

00:08:02.240 --> 00:08:03.480
Isolated from the world,

00:08:03.480 --> 00:08:05.130
And lived inside the mountains.

00:08:05.130 --> 00:08:06.310
Until one day,

00:08:06.650 --> 00:08:08.560
Their ancestors dug out a huge black stone

00:08:08.560 --> 00:08:10.480
From the mountain,

00:08:10.600 --> 00:08:11.920
Which completely changed the life

00:08:11.920 --> 00:08:13.430
Of the whole tribe.

00:08:13.720 --> 00:08:14.950
To be exact,

00:08:15.100 --> 00:08:17.690
This stone somehow affected them,

00:08:18.250 --> 00:08:20.210
Making them bloody and brutal.

00:08:20.270 --> 00:08:22.810
Their physical functions also became exceptionally strong,

00:08:22.810 --> 00:08:25.270
Able to heal themselves without treatment,

00:08:25.300 --> 00:08:26.700
And even come back to life

00:08:26.770 --> 00:08:27.720
After death.

00:08:28.080 --> 00:08:29.720
The medicine that made Shrimpie

00:08:29.720 --> 00:08:31.410
Recover and go crazy

00:08:32.000 --> 00:08:33.789
Came from this black stone.

00:08:36.580 --> 00:08:37.370
No, wait.

00:08:37.530 --> 00:08:38.929
Didn't you tell me before

00:08:39.500 --> 00:08:41.970
That it was some kind of worm from jellyfish?

00:08:42.890 --> 00:08:44.140
Maybe this thing

00:08:46.010 --> 00:08:47.830
Originated from here.

00:08:54.000 --> 00:08:56.400
The black stones are irradiating the soil,

00:08:56.750 --> 00:08:58.590
Causing a parasite to mutate.

00:09:01.240 --> 00:09:03.050
It's the worm Mentor mentioned,

00:09:03.870 --> 00:09:05.170
Called Caiyou worms.

00:09:06.910 --> 00:09:08.570
All parasitized creatures

00:09:09.120 --> 00:09:11.780
Will also undergo varying degrees of mutation.

00:09:12.100 --> 00:09:13.700
Among them, infected people

00:09:13.960 --> 00:09:15.130
Become physically strong

00:09:15.130 --> 00:09:16.640
And are called Atianre,

00:09:19.150 --> 00:09:19.900
Meaning

00:09:21.770 --> 00:09:22.960
"the Chosen One".

00:09:24.480 --> 00:09:26.680
After the tribe dug out the black stone,

00:09:27.230 --> 00:09:29.090
The Caiyou worms began to spread.

00:09:32.390 --> 00:09:34.050
It made snakes grow black hair

00:09:34.940 --> 00:09:36.470
And speak human language.

00:09:39.280 --> 00:09:41.340
It also turned grass into toxic weed.

00:09:42.950 --> 00:09:45.950
All parasitized creatures have one characteristic,

00:09:48.650 --> 00:09:51.310
Which is that they can hibernate for a long time.

00:09:52.120 --> 00:09:54.580
This is the so-called suspended animation.

00:09:54.630 --> 00:09:56.160
So the black-haired snakes

00:09:57.000 --> 00:09:59.400
And Twilight Grass all come from Nanqiang.

00:10:00.390 --> 00:10:02.940
They mutated after being infected with worms.

00:10:02.940 --> 00:10:04.320
No wonder the Twilight Grass

00:10:04.320 --> 00:10:05.600
Grows so luxuriantly here.

00:10:05.600 --> 00:10:06.890
It seems these ancient Wupi people

00:10:06.890 --> 00:10:08.990
Discovered these natural phenomena

00:10:09.080 --> 00:10:10.210
And made use of them,

00:10:10.750 --> 00:10:12.150
Using them as weapons

00:10:12.480 --> 00:10:13.860
To wipe out other tribes

00:10:14.100 --> 00:10:16.500
And continuously expand their territory.

00:10:17.030 --> 00:10:17.770
But this tribe

00:10:17.770 --> 00:10:19.380
Has no records or legends.

00:10:20.530 --> 00:10:22.860
It must have disappeared for some reason.

00:10:28.530 --> 00:10:29.990
The reason should be here.

00:10:31.410 --> 00:10:33.390
In fact, the behavior of these Atianre

00:10:33.390 --> 00:10:34.990
Was controlled by the worms.

00:10:38.320 --> 00:10:41.120
These Atianre seemed to have two consciousnesses

00:10:43.940 --> 00:10:46.620
Fighting each other in the same body.

00:10:50.500 --> 00:10:51.100
In the end,

00:10:51.720 --> 00:10:54.120
They became completely brutal and bloody,

00:10:54.860 --> 00:10:57.320
Turning into completely different people.

00:11:04.750 --> 00:11:06.110
So what you did

00:11:09.000 --> 00:11:10.530
Was not your intention.

00:11:19.920 --> 00:11:21.650
What's more terrifying is that

00:11:21.870 --> 00:11:23.400
Over time,

00:11:23.650 --> 00:11:24.780
These Atianre

00:11:25.030 --> 00:11:27.150
Would eventually turn into monsters

00:11:27.700 --> 00:11:29.500
Because of the worm's power.

00:11:30.010 --> 00:11:32.610
And all creatures infected with Caiyou worms,

00:11:33.600 --> 00:11:35.650
Like mantises infected with horsehair worms

00:11:35.650 --> 00:11:37.390
That must enter the water,

00:11:37.940 --> 00:11:39.280
Will desperately

00:11:39.630 --> 00:11:41.630
Want to return to the meteorite.

00:11:41.950 --> 00:11:43.880
The occurrence of this phenomenon

00:11:44.250 --> 00:11:46.250
Made the people in the tribe realize

00:11:46.530 --> 00:11:47.270
That Atianre

00:11:47.270 --> 00:11:49.520
Did not gain any good power.

00:11:50.080 --> 00:11:50.790
Its essence

00:11:51.320 --> 00:11:52.520
Was actually a devil.

00:11:53.270 --> 00:11:54.460
So the ancient people

00:11:54.460 --> 00:11:55.300
And Atianre

00:11:56.000 --> 00:11:57.130
Went to war.

00:12:03.200 --> 00:12:05.090
The kind ancient Wupi people

00:12:05.290 --> 00:12:07.410
Were almost all killed by the cruel Atianre,

00:12:07.410 --> 00:12:09.670
The ones who worshipped the black stone.

00:12:13.070 --> 00:12:14.730
However, it didn't end there.

00:12:19.700 --> 00:12:20.830
The Zhang family...

00:12:22.320 --> 00:12:23.710
Our ancestors

00:12:23.840 --> 00:12:25.290
Noticed something strange in Nanqiang,

00:12:25.290 --> 00:12:27.220
And helped the ancient Wupi people

00:12:27.250 --> 00:12:29.050
Fight against the evil Atianre.

00:12:29.580 --> 00:12:31.270
These ghost-like creatures

00:12:31.910 --> 00:12:33.840
Fled all the way to the black stone.

00:12:34.790 --> 00:12:36.860
They, along with the black stone,

00:12:36.890 --> 00:12:40.150
Were sealed in a Bronze Ball Mechanism by the Zhang family.

00:12:42.250 --> 00:12:43.870
They never appeared again.

00:12:45.460 --> 00:12:47.930
An earthquake in Nanqiang 20 years ago

00:12:48.580 --> 00:12:50.700
Loosened the seal of the Bronze Ball Mechanism,

00:12:50.700 --> 00:12:52.230
And many monsters escaped.

00:12:53.910 --> 00:12:55.840
The current chief came to handle it

00:12:55.860 --> 00:12:57.370
And sealed it again.

00:13:01.240 --> 00:13:02.200
I see.

00:13:02.990 --> 00:13:03.940
So Dark Shrimp's goal

00:13:03.940 --> 00:13:06.270
Is to open the Bronze Ball Mechanism again

00:13:06.390 --> 00:13:07.990
And return to the meteorite.

00:13:08.480 --> 00:13:09.080
Yes.

00:13:10.290 --> 00:13:13.050
Behind Dark Shrimp is the consciousness of the Caiyou worms.

00:13:13.050 --> 00:13:15.390
Opening the Bronze Ball Mechanism is its instinct.

00:13:15.390 --> 00:13:17.920
But once the Bronze Ball Mechanism is opened,

00:13:18.030 --> 00:13:20.790
All the creatures sealed inside will come out.

00:13:22.480 --> 00:13:23.390
If so,

00:13:24.080 --> 00:13:25.170
Not only Nanqiang,

00:13:25.500 --> 00:13:27.360
But everyone will be threatened.

00:13:28.120 --> 00:13:29.240
If people are parasitized

00:13:29.240 --> 00:13:30.790
By the things on this stone,

00:13:31.320 --> 00:13:33.720
They will become bloodthirsty and brutal.

00:13:42.150 --> 00:13:44.280
First, it's consciousness invasion.

00:13:44.960 --> 00:13:46.420
Eventually, they undergo

00:13:47.050 --> 00:13:51.180
A complete mutation into monsters resembling human-headed centipedes.

00:14:01.910 --> 00:14:03.640
Twilight Grass and the Evil God

00:14:04.940 --> 00:14:07.670
Are enough to turn the outside world upside down.

00:14:08.030 --> 00:14:08.980
Such monsters

00:14:10.510 --> 00:14:12.460
Had better die underground.

00:14:34.600 --> 00:14:35.320
Mentor.

00:14:38.370 --> 00:14:39.360
Traitor.

00:14:43.540 --> 00:14:46.340
Do you think what you burned was the real medicine?

00:15:08.320 --> 00:15:09.270
Zhang Haixia,

00:15:11.170 --> 00:15:12.620
I want to rest.

00:15:17.150 --> 00:15:18.480
Help me end this.

00:15:20.530 --> 00:15:22.460
I'll wait for you on the other side.

00:15:49.720 --> 00:15:51.360
You never give me peace.

00:15:55.800 --> 00:15:58.690
Do you think what you burned was the real medicine?

00:18:12.660 --> 00:18:13.290
Shrimpie.

00:18:19.070 --> 00:18:19.870
Zhang Hailou,

00:18:20.940 --> 00:18:21.880
Can you hold on?

00:18:41.320 --> 00:18:43.650
Someone is detonating explosives below.

00:18:44.240 --> 00:18:45.380
It's Zhang Haixia.

00:18:45.640 --> 00:18:47.370
He needs to go deep underground

00:18:47.790 --> 00:18:48.940
To find something sealed by

00:18:48.940 --> 00:18:50.040
The Zhang ancestors

00:18:50.040 --> 00:18:51.840
And release the monster inside.

00:19:04.820 --> 00:19:06.160
Where are you going?

00:19:06.420 --> 00:19:07.660
I have to stop him.

00:19:07.980 --> 00:19:09.110
How will you do that?

00:19:09.110 --> 00:19:10.320
I don't know yet.

00:19:33.400 --> 00:19:34.160
You go first.

00:19:34.190 --> 00:19:35.470
We'll catch up later.

00:20:01.830 --> 00:20:03.510
It's dangerous, go!

00:20:04.900 --> 00:20:05.970
Hold on to me.

00:20:07.570 --> 00:20:09.960
Let go, or you'll die!

00:20:09.980 --> 00:20:10.780
Hold on tight.

00:20:11.250 --> 00:20:12.710
I won't let go even if I die.

00:20:15.740 --> 00:20:17.470
Do you really like me that much?

00:20:19.510 --> 00:20:20.460
I do.

00:20:23.240 --> 00:20:24.510
Then if we make it out,

00:20:25.590 --> 00:20:26.740
Will you marry me?

00:21:18.590 --> 00:21:19.520
Adjutant Zhang,

00:21:20.240 --> 00:21:22.500
Is this the secret deep within Nanqiang?

00:21:22.650 --> 00:21:24.050
What exactly is in there?

00:21:25.110 --> 00:21:27.040
Your mission is already complete.

00:23:56.510 --> 00:23:57.700
You're not dead?

00:23:59.130 --> 00:24:01.130
How could I bear to die before you do?

00:24:58.530 --> 00:25:00.530
You want to use Zhang Haixia's blood

00:25:01.440 --> 00:25:03.240
To open the Zhang family's seal.

00:25:04.960 --> 00:25:06.310
He is special.

00:25:09.660 --> 00:25:11.640
But his willpower was so strong,

00:25:11.670 --> 00:25:12.840
And he was so clever,

00:25:14.480 --> 00:25:15.920
I have to erase him.

00:25:17.210 --> 00:25:18.270
Zhang Hailou.

00:25:18.850 --> 00:25:19.920
If you kill me,

00:25:21.640 --> 00:25:23.180
He will die too.

00:25:28.480 --> 00:25:29.340
You are not him.

00:25:31.920 --> 00:25:32.980
Don't call my name.

00:27:41.270 --> 00:27:43.130
Do you want to go back to Xiacheng?

00:27:48.430 --> 00:27:52.280
♪ The setting sun sinks low into the sea ♪

00:27:49.560 --> 00:27:51.220
Do you want to go back to Xiacheng?

00:27:51.220 --> 00:27:52.620
Nonsense, of course I do.

00:27:54.240 --> 00:27:55.070
Go back to Xiacheng

00:27:54.560 --> 00:27:57.200
♪ And the ship goes down into the flames ♪

00:27:55.550 --> 00:27:56.680
And find our mentor.

00:27:57.900 --> 00:27:58.590
Leave me alone!

00:27:58.550 --> 00:28:01.090
♪ You're standing by my side ♪

00:27:59.300 --> 00:28:00.390
Follow me.

00:28:00.440 --> 00:28:02.760
We'll make a name for ourselves in Balongzhou.

00:28:02.760 --> 00:28:04.270
Then we'll return to Xiacheng in glory

00:28:04.270 --> 00:28:05.850
And see Mentor together. Let's go!

00:28:04.390 --> 00:28:08.190
♪ Time is like a plague, devouring yesterday ♪

00:28:06.270 --> 00:28:07.700
Zhang Haixia, what are you doing?

00:28:07.700 --> 00:28:09.520
I don't want to go back to Xiacheng.

00:28:09.520 --> 00:28:11.140
I have nothing left to hold me there.

00:28:10.330 --> 00:28:12.840
♪ Yet I've searched through every archive ♪

00:28:11.570 --> 00:28:12.740
Go back in my place.

00:28:14.590 --> 00:28:16.290
♪ Filled with endless lies ♪

00:28:14.700 --> 00:28:16.300
We still came back together.

00:28:17.000 --> 00:28:18.530
You shouldn't have come back to save me.

00:28:18.300 --> 00:28:20.240
♪ Even behind a thousand masks ♪

00:28:19.750 --> 00:28:21.030
Didn't you save me too?

00:28:20.650 --> 00:28:24.790
♪ In a fleeting moment, I fear a familiar face ♪

00:28:21.940 --> 00:28:22.940
You are my junior.

00:28:23.960 --> 00:28:25.680
It's my duty to keep you safe.

00:28:26.350 --> 00:28:28.180
♪ Fate got one thing wrong ♪

00:28:28.880 --> 00:28:32.450
♪ Beneath the setting sun, our shadows overlap ♪

00:28:30.080 --> 00:28:31.530
[Nanyang Maritime Supervisory Office]

00:28:30.400 --> 00:28:31.050
Hailou,

00:28:32.530 --> 00:28:33.460
One day

00:28:34.410 --> 00:28:38.540
♪ The wind carries away the goodbye we never said ♪

00:28:34.790 --> 00:28:36.450
You'll have to act on your own.

00:28:37.580 --> 00:28:38.840
I won't be by your side.

00:28:39.370 --> 00:28:42.160
♪ The butterfly upon your shoulder ♪

00:28:40.440 --> 00:28:42.240
No one will be watching over you.

00:28:42.980 --> 00:28:49.150
♪ Stayed with you to witness this bustling world ♪

00:28:50.490 --> 00:28:54.700
♪ Where ruin and decay begin to turn around ♪

00:28:55.380 --> 00:28:58.290
♪ A gut feeling of destiny ♪

00:28:57.860 --> 00:29:01.490
[iKiwi Film Company]

00:28:58.870 --> 00:29:04.930
♪ Bright sunlight, unseen mountains and seas ♪

00:29:06.110 --> 00:29:06.900
Thank you.

00:29:22.370 --> 00:29:23.610
I'm a little tired.

00:29:24.300 --> 00:29:28.380
♪ A reckless faith, blurred from sight ♪

00:29:30.490 --> 00:29:33.400
