00:29:38.960 --> 00:29:40.560
The xia from "xia ke" (hero).

00:29:40.640 --> 00:29:44.780
♪ Bound to the prophecy of thrush and snake ♪

00:29:40.710 --> 00:29:41.990
And he's Zhang Hailou—

00:29:42.350 --> 00:29:44.000
The lou from "louyu" (building).

00:29:44.000 --> 00:29:45.860
A tower in spring rain overnight.

00:29:46.220 --> 00:29:47.810
Xianyang wanderers, years gone by.

00:29:46.330 --> 00:29:48.280
♪ Yet suddenly before my eyes ♪

00:29:48.690 --> 00:29:52.430
♪ That hurried goodbye ♪

00:29:54.650 --> 00:29:58.800
♪ The opening pages of this story are woven from deceit ♪

00:29:59.320 --> 00:30:02.240
♪ A trial written into fate ♪

00:30:02.990 --> 00:30:09.040
♪ Through the mist I search your face— are you still the same? ♪

00:30:10.460 --> 00:30:14.800
♪ The wind carries away the goodbye we never said ♪

00:30:15.320 --> 00:30:18.390
♪ The butterfly upon your shoulder ♪

00:30:18.780 --> 00:30:24.700
♪ Stayed with you to witness this bustling world ♪

00:31:04.100 --> 00:31:06.480
[A few days later]

00:31:35.310 --> 00:31:38.590
[Soul-Cleansing Temple]

00:31:53.680 --> 00:31:54.940
Why are you here?

00:32:04.700 --> 00:32:05.880
I was a bit curious,

00:32:06.770 --> 00:32:08.030
So I did some research.

00:32:09.180 --> 00:32:11.040
What exactly is that black stone,

00:32:11.950 --> 00:32:14.080
And what is controlling Zhang Haixia?

00:32:14.200 --> 00:32:15.460
Did you find anything?

00:32:25.330 --> 00:32:27.440
The strange star is three feet across,

00:32:27.440 --> 00:32:29.090
Shaped like a round jade,

00:32:29.110 --> 00:32:30.710
And colored like black jade.

00:32:42.720 --> 00:32:43.610
What does that mean?

00:32:42.950 --> 00:32:43.750
[Three Generations—Star Guide Chronicles, Vol. 1]

00:32:43.900 --> 00:32:45.440
I guess that black stone

00:32:45.550 --> 00:32:47.010
Is very likely a meteorite

00:32:47.400 --> 00:32:49.460
That fell from the sky a long time ago.

00:32:49.810 --> 00:32:50.680
A meteorite?

00:32:51.050 --> 00:32:52.590
Three-corpse bugs reside in the Big Dipper;

00:32:52.590 --> 00:32:55.320
When stars fall, the bugs enter the mortal realm.

00:32:58.050 --> 00:32:59.330
Actually, among these books,

00:32:59.330 --> 00:33:00.860
Many are about meteorites.

00:33:03.220 --> 00:33:04.010
I suspect

00:33:05.070 --> 00:33:06.730
The Caiyou worms on the murals

00:33:07.030 --> 00:33:09.290
Are the alien bugs brought by the meteorite.

00:33:09.290 --> 00:33:11.090
They have parasitic abilities.

00:33:11.420 --> 00:33:12.420
When they parasitize

00:33:12.420 --> 00:33:13.440
A living creature,

00:33:13.440 --> 00:33:15.610
They can also help repair its damaged body.

00:33:15.610 --> 00:33:17.070
But there's a side effect.

00:33:17.510 --> 00:33:20.250
That is, they will disrupt the host's nervous system.

00:33:20.250 --> 00:33:21.780
And this new consciousness

00:33:22.140 --> 00:33:24.600
Gradually erodes the host's original mind,

00:33:25.610 --> 00:33:27.270
Eventually becoming the new dominant consciousness.

00:33:27.270 --> 00:33:28.290
Like

00:33:28.980 --> 00:33:30.110
A cuckoo in the nest?

00:33:34.900 --> 00:33:35.530
Then,

00:33:36.250 --> 00:33:38.960
Zhang Haixia insisting on returning to Nanqiang earlier

00:33:38.960 --> 00:33:40.360
Was also because of this?

00:33:40.400 --> 00:33:42.400
This might have something to do with

00:33:43.440 --> 00:33:44.940
The homing instinct of these alien bugs.

00:33:44.940 --> 00:33:46.640
Perhaps these alien bugs have

00:33:47.900 --> 00:33:49.900
A survival instinct to return home.

00:33:50.200 --> 00:33:51.030
That's why

00:33:51.030 --> 00:33:53.160
He wanted to come to Nanqiang so badly.

00:34:01.440 --> 00:34:03.380
Where are you going? I'll go with you.

00:34:03.380 --> 00:34:04.180
To the toilet.

00:34:04.480 --> 00:34:05.680
Do you want to follow?

00:34:06.850 --> 00:34:07.450
By the way,

00:34:07.510 --> 00:34:09.030
The black-haired snake you mentioned earlier,

00:34:09.030 --> 00:34:10.460
Did it get on you by accident,

00:34:10.460 --> 00:34:13.190
Or was it deliberately arranged by Zhang Haixia?

00:34:16.280 --> 00:34:17.000
Who knows.

00:34:19.260 --> 00:34:21.320
I'm getting married. Are you coming?

00:34:21.380 --> 00:34:22.280
Are you coming?

00:34:26.510 --> 00:34:28.969
-A happy marriage and kids soon! -Kids soon!

00:34:32.360 --> 00:34:34.150
Wish you happiness!

00:34:42.860 --> 00:34:43.590
Happy.

00:34:43.590 --> 00:34:45.300
Thank you.

00:34:46.480 --> 00:34:47.300
One more round!

00:34:47.300 --> 00:34:48.110
One more round!

00:34:48.110 --> 00:34:49.010
One more round!

00:34:50.440 --> 00:34:51.300
One more round!

00:34:51.460 --> 00:34:52.370
One more round!

00:34:52.670 --> 00:34:53.420
One more round!

00:34:53.370 --> 00:34:59.290
♪ The past fades into traces on the page ♪

00:34:55.000 --> 00:34:56.440
Kids soon!

00:34:57.070 --> 00:34:58.480
Congratulations.

00:34:58.940 --> 00:34:59.670
From now on,

00:35:00.460 --> 00:35:06.240
♪ A silent breeze brushes past that lingering warmth ♪

00:35:00.570 --> 00:35:03.480
You have to carry me on your back for the rest of your life.

00:35:03.480 --> 00:35:04.210
Definitely.

00:35:06.960 --> 00:35:07.690
Let the feast begin.

00:35:07.560 --> 00:35:13.620
♪ In this fleeting world, I long for a moment of vivid life ♪

00:35:08.210 --> 00:35:08.630
Let the feast begin.

00:35:08.630 --> 00:35:09.110
Let the feast begin.

00:35:09.110 --> 00:35:10.240
Let the feast begin.

00:35:14.580 --> 00:35:19.370
♪ I may have a chance to open a door ♪

00:35:19.940 --> 00:35:20.500
Come.

00:35:20.500 --> 00:35:20.880
Here.

00:35:20.650 --> 00:35:27.350
♪ Where love and wish meet in a fleeting moment ♪

00:35:20.960 --> 00:35:22.030
Happy wedding!

00:35:22.030 --> 00:35:22.860
Cheers.

00:35:22.860 --> 00:35:23.730
Drink up!

00:35:27.920 --> 00:35:34.220
♪ There's no need to ask questions in the maze ♪

00:35:34.010 --> 00:35:34.760
Eat, eat

00:35:34.820 --> 00:35:37.190
♪ The world's bustle ♪

00:35:34.960 --> 00:35:36.380
Come, eat up.

00:35:36.500 --> 00:35:37.230
Don't be shy.

00:35:37.630 --> 00:35:42.630
♪ For now, a few of us under the same roof ♪

00:35:38.260 --> 00:35:39.390
Let's go over there.

00:35:43.620 --> 00:35:49.310
♪ And the story has come to an end ♪

00:35:44.550 --> 00:35:45.300
Snake charmer,

00:35:45.300 --> 00:35:46.230
Shouldn't we have a drink?

00:35:46.230 --> 00:35:47.340
Absolutely.

00:35:47.370 --> 00:35:47.690
Cheers.

00:35:47.690 --> 00:35:48.150
Cheers.

00:35:48.980 --> 00:35:49.840
One more drink.

00:35:51.320 --> 00:35:53.250
Aren't you going to ask him to stay?

00:35:59.650 --> 00:36:00.650
I didn't expect

00:36:00.830 --> 00:36:02.490
Everything he said to be true.

00:36:02.780 --> 00:36:04.070
He had a very good,

00:36:04.480 --> 00:36:05.570
Great friend.

00:36:04.810 --> 00:36:08.010
♪ Clouds drift and fade just a few years ♪

00:36:06.710 --> 00:36:08.280
It's hard to imagine what Zhang Haixia

00:36:08.280 --> 00:36:09.490
Has been through.

00:36:10.690 --> 00:36:11.990
It must be painful.

00:36:11.880 --> 00:36:15.100
♪ Mortal world grass regrows after parting ♪

00:36:13.800 --> 00:36:15.400
The one left behind at the end

00:36:16.980 --> 00:36:18.110
Suffers the most.

00:36:26.900 --> 00:36:29.830
[Years later]

00:36:56.020 --> 00:36:57.680
There's trouble in Nanqiang.

00:36:58.000 --> 00:36:59.600
We need to work together.

00:37:00.450 --> 00:37:03.450
I'm looking forward to fighting alongside you again.

00:37:45.840 --> 00:37:47.980
Mentor, Zhang Haichan is the one who made the mistake.

00:37:47.360 --> 00:37:49.080
[Zhang Haichan] [Zhang Haidou]

00:37:48.010 --> 00:37:49.420
Why are you punishing me?

00:37:49.780 --> 00:37:50.900
You are the senior brother.

00:37:50.900 --> 00:37:52.500
Her mistake is your mistake.

00:37:52.690 --> 00:37:54.210
You need to protect your junior sister, got it?

00:37:54.210 --> 00:37:55.800
I am younger than her.

00:37:56.400 --> 00:37:58.730
Who told you to become a disciple earlier?

00:37:59.510 --> 00:38:01.230
I must have sinned in my past life

00:38:01.230 --> 00:38:02.730
To have a junior sister like you.

00:38:02.730 --> 00:38:04.070
In the future when I go on missions,

00:38:04.070 --> 00:38:05.940
I will definitely stay far away from you.

00:38:05.940 --> 00:38:07.870
I want to stay far away from you too.

00:38:07.870 --> 00:38:09.610
I want to stay far away from you.

00:38:09.630 --> 00:38:10.300
-I want to -Come on, keep up!

00:38:10.300 --> 00:38:12.550
-stay far away from you. -I want to stay far away from you.

00:38:12.550 --> 00:38:14.670
-I want to stay far away from you. -I want to stay far away from you.

00:38:14.670 --> 00:38:15.380
Stay away from me!

00:38:15.380 --> 00:38:18.980
-I want to stay far away from you. -I want to stay far away from you.

00:38:24.760 --> 00:38:26.090
Haichan, Haidou,

00:38:27.550 --> 00:38:29.280
Don't forget what I taught you.

00:38:29.340 --> 00:38:31.290
Greet them properly when we see them later.

00:38:31.290 --> 00:38:31.850
Okay.

00:38:39.500 --> 00:38:41.090
Greetings, chief!

00:38:41.190 --> 00:38:41.840
Chief.

00:38:53.710 --> 00:38:55.550
Something's happened deep in Nanqiang.

00:38:55.550 --> 00:38:56.680
It's time to set off.

00:38:56.760 --> 00:38:57.820
Let's set off.

00:39:55.670 --> 00:39:59.850
[Wushan Residence]

00:40:04.160 --> 00:40:08.140
[Wu Xie]

00:40:05.800 --> 00:40:07.490
The story of the Southern Archives

00:40:07.490 --> 00:40:09.220
Has temporarily come to an end.

00:40:09.860 --> 00:40:10.920
After watching it,

00:40:10.960 --> 00:40:11.960
I am just like you,

00:40:12.130 --> 00:40:14.060
Unable to calm down for a long time.

00:40:16.170 --> 00:40:20.790
[Closing Report: Nanyang Balai Yazhou Salt-Alkali Lake]

00:40:16.210 --> 00:40:17.260
My soul

00:40:17.480 --> 00:40:18.400
Seems to have stayed in

00:40:18.400 --> 00:40:19.880
That sunny Nanyang,

00:40:20.280 --> 00:40:22.170
That magnificent Bailejing,

00:40:20.940 --> 00:40:26.350
[Closing Report: Nanqiang Bailejing]

00:40:22.420 --> 00:40:23.620
Unwilling to return.

00:40:26.350 --> 00:40:33.190
[Closing Report: Panhua Reef]

00:40:40.460 --> 00:40:41.340
Has their story

00:40:41.610 --> 00:40:42.730
Ended here?

00:40:46.970 --> 00:40:47.910
Or,

00:40:49.030 --> 00:40:50.770
Will we be able to meet again?

00:41:00.900 --> 00:41:01.530
I think,

00:41:02.050 --> 00:41:04.010
In the process of digging into the past,

00:41:04.010 --> 00:41:05.740
We will definitely meet again.

00:41:05.940 --> 00:41:08.340
I will definitely see their legends again.

00:41:09.440 --> 00:41:10.090
However,

00:41:10.550 --> 00:41:12.880
Do you still want to keep watching with me?

